metadata.name: WAD.THE (VILLAIN)HERO
metadata.description: "WAD.HERO" from another galaxy who was branded as a villain "HERO" on the human sight. He tried to gather a WAD Coin for years with no explain what did he actually do. He didn't even care how damaged the building and the surrounding area,  He still gather the WAD Coin scattered around the world. Although he destroyed many buildings, still no any reported for injured... WHO ARE YOU WAD.HERO!!??
